{"parse":{"title":"'Tis So Sweet to Trust in Jesus","pageid":18642308,"revid":859815960,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vevent haudio\" style=\"width:22em\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"summary album\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">'Tis So Sweet to Trust in Jesus</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:WilliamJKirkpatrick.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"WilliamJKirkpatrick.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/WilliamJKirkpatrick.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"307\" data-file-width=\"200\" data-file-height=\"307\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Hymn\" title=\"Hymn\">Hymn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Text</th><td>\nLouisa M. R. Stead</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Based on</th><td>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Bible_(King_James)/Isaiah#12:2\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Bible (King James)/Isaiah\">Isaiah&#32;12&#58;2</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Meter</th><td>\n8.7.8.7 with refrain</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Melody</th><td>\n\"Trust in Jesus\" by <a href=\"/wiki/William_J._Kirkpatrick\" title=\"William J. Kirkpatrick\">William J. Kirkpatrick</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Published</th><td>\n1882</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><div class=\"mediaContainer\" style=\"width:220px\"><audio id=\"mwe_player_0\" controls=\"\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width:220px\" class=\"kskin\" data-durationhint=\"35.004081632653\" data-startoffset=\"0\" data-mwtitle=\"Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus.ogg\" data-mwprovider=\"wikimediacommons\"><source src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d8/Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg; codecs=&quot;vorbis&quot;\" data-title=\"Original Ogg file (105 kbps)\" data-shorttitle=\"Ogg source\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\" data-bandwidth=\"105367\" /><source src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/transcoded/d/d8/Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus.ogg/Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus.ogg.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\" data-title=\"MP3\" data-shorttitle=\"MP3\" data-transcodekey=\"mp3\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\" data-bandwidth=\"174520\" /></audio></div>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus.ogg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tis So Sweet to Trust in Jesus</div></div></div>\n<p>\"'<b>Tis So Sweet to Trust in Jesus</b>\" is a <a href=\"/wiki/Christian\" title=\"Christian\">Christian</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Hymn\" title=\"Hymn\">hymn</a> with music by <a href=\"/wiki/William_J._Kirkpatrick\" title=\"William J. Kirkpatrick\">William J. Kirkpatrick</a> and lyrics by Louisa M. R. Stead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The lyrics were written in 1882. They appeared in Stead's <i>Songs of Triumph</i>.\n</p><p>The song is included in many hymnals and has been recorded by many artists.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lyrics\">Lyrics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=%27Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Lyrics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"poem\">\n<p>\u2019Tis so sweet to trust in Jesus,<br />\nJust to take Him at His Word;<br />\nJust to rest upon His promise,<br />\nJust to know, \"Thus says the Lord!\"<br />\n<br />\nRefrain<br />\nJesus, Jesus, how I trust Him!<br />\nHow I\u2019ve proved Him o\u2019er and o\u2019er<br />\nJesus, Jesus, precious Jesus!<br />\nO for grace to trust Him more!<br />\n<br />\nO how sweet to trust in Jesus,<br />\nJust to trust His cleansing blood;<br />\nJust in simple faith to plunge me<br />\n\u2019Neath the healing, cleansing flood!<br />\n<br />\nRefrain<br />\n<br />\nYes, \u2019tis sweet to trust in Jesus,<br />\nJust from sin and self to cease;<br />\nJust from Jesus simply taking<br />\nLife and rest, and joy and peace.<br />\n<br />\nRefrain<br />\n<br />\nI\u2019m so glad I learned to trust Thee,<br />\nPrecious Jesus, Savior, Friend;<br />\nAnd I know that Thou art with me,<br />\nWilt be with me to the end.<br />\n<br />\nRefrain\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=%27Tis_So_Sweet_to_Trust_in_Jesus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Osbeck, Kenneth (1985). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=rQ_Y078X5NAC&amp;pg=PA287&amp;lpg=PA91#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\"><i>101 More Hymn Stories, Part 2</i></a>. Kregel Publications. p.&#160;91.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=101+More+Hymn+Stories%2C+Part+2&amp;rft.pages=91&amp;rft.pub=Kregel+Publications&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.aulast=Osbeck&amp;rft.aufirst=Kenneth&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DrQ_Y078X5NAC%26pg%3DPA287%26lpg%3DPA91%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A%27Tis+So+Sweet+to+Trust+in+Jesus\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-